534
00:25:49,634 --> 00:25:54,234
But when you're an adult,
you really get to enjoy it.

535
00:25:55,133 --> 00:25:59,100
Let's say you work all day,
you're on your way home,

536
00:25:59,167 --> 00:26:02,000
you're really tired.

537
00:26:02,067 --> 00:26:04,334
It's that really good kind of tired,

538
00:26:04,400 --> 00:26:06,934
where you know
that you're on your way home.

539
00:26:07,000 --> 00:26:09,167
Soon you're gonna be at your home.

540
00:26:09,234 --> 00:26:12,000
You're gonna be by yourself
for a little bit.

541
00:26:12,067 --> 00:26:15,400
You get home, you go to your fridge,

542
00:26:15,467 --> 00:26:20,467
You get yourself a bottle of beer.

543
00:26:20,534 --> 00:26:23,100
It's ice cold.

544
00:26:23,167 --> 00:26:24,834
You open it up

545
00:26:24,901 --> 00:26:27,400
and it makes that great sound,
that hissing sound.

546
00:26:27,467 --> 00:26:31,534
Even the cap hitting the counter
makes a great sound.

547
00:26:31,601 --> 00:26:35,133
Go to your living room,
sit down on the couch,

548
00:26:35,200 --> 00:26:38,000
bring that bottle up to your lips.

549
00:26:38,067 --> 00:26:40,334
You can smell that smell,
that beer smell.

550
00:26:40,400 --> 00:26:43,567
It reminds you of what beer smelled
like to you when you were a little kid.

551
00:26:43,634 --> 00:26:45,434
You didn't like the taste of beer.

552
00:26:45,500 --> 00:26:47,234
But now it's a fond memory.

553
00:26:47,300 --> 00:26:48,801
Remembering when you were a little kid

554
00:26:48,868 --> 00:26:50,667
and things were really simple,

555
00:26:50,734 --> 00:26:52,434
and you didn't like the taste of beer.

556
00:26:52,500 --> 00:26:57,167
but now you're a grown-up,
you take a sip.

557
00:26:57,234 --> 00:27:00,200
It really tastes like beer.

558
00:27:00,267 --> 00:27:02,067
You've had plenty of beers
in your life.

559
00:27:02,133 --> 00:27:05,901
But this one reminds you
of what beer tastes like.

560
00:27:05,968 --> 00:27:09,500
Kind of sharp on your tongue,
a little bitter.

561
00:27:09,567 --> 00:27:11,801
It's so cold.

562
00:27:11,868 --> 00:27:17,267
There's nothing else like it,
a nice cold beer.

563
00:27:39,067 --> 00:27:41,267
You're allowed to have it.

564
00:27:48,133 --> 00:27:51,334
Just make sure you eat first.

